About

Death's Door Marine is uniquely capable to handle every aspect of your marine construction needs. We professionally engineer solutions for marine environments AND build what we design. Owner Mike Kahr is a professional civil engineer who has been building and designing docks in Door County for over 30 years. Mike is considered a statewide expert in marine contstruction and the permiting process for marine structures on Lake Michigan. An example of his experitise can be seen in the multiple patents he holds for his innovative dock designs, which are designed to be raised, lowered, and fully withstanding of winter ice. Give us a call today for a free consultation.
